column2: SELECT TOP # g.objid, g.run, g.rerun, g.camcol, g.field, g.obj, g.ra, g.dec, g.clean, g.petroMag_u, g.petroMag_g, g.petroMag_r, g.petroMag_i, g.petroMag_z, g.petroRad_u, g.petroRad_g, g.petroRad_r, g.petroRad_i, g.petroRad_z, g.petroR5#_u, g.petroR5#_g, g.petroR5#_r, g.petroR5#_i, g.petroR5#_z, g.petroR9#_u, g.petroR9#_g, g.petroR9#_r, g.petroR9#_i, g.petroR9#_z, g.deVRad_u, g.deVRad_g, g.deVRad_r, g.deVRad_i, g.deVRad_z, g.deVMag_u, g.deVMag_g, g.deVMag_r, g.deVMag_i, g.deVMag_z, g.expRad_u, g.expRad_g, g.expRad_r, g.expRad_i, g.expRad_z, g.expMag_u, g.expMag_g, g.expMag_r, g.expMag_i, g.expMag_z, g.modelMag_u, g.modelMag_g, g.modelMag_r, g.modelMag_i, g.modelMag_z, g.cModelMag_u, g.cModelMag_g, g.cModelMag_r, g.cModelMag_i, g.cModelMag_z, g.q_u as stokes_q_u, g.q_g as stokes_q_g, g.q_r as stokes_q_r, g.q_i as stokes_q_i, g.q_z as stokes_q_z, g.u_u as stokes_u_u, g.u_g as stokes_u_g, g.u_r as stokes_u_r, g.u_i as stokes_u_i, g.u_z as stokes_u_z, g.extinction_u, g.extinction_g, g.extinction_r, g.extinction_i, g.extinction_z, sp.z, sp.zErr, zs.nvote as votes, zs.p_el as elliptical, zs.p_cw as spiralclock, zs.p_acw as spiralanticlock, zs.p_edge as edgeon, zs.p_dk as dontknow, zs.p_mg as merger, zs.p_el_debiased as debiased_elliptical, zs.p_cs_debiased as debiased_spiral, zs.spiral as debiased_spiral_ind, zs.elliptical as debiased_elliptical_ind, zs.uncertain as debiased_uncertain_ind FROM Galaxy as G JOIN ZooSpec AS zs ON G.objid = zs.objid JOIN SpecPhoto as sp ON sp.objID = zs.objid WHERE g.clean = #
